            <lg xml:id="TK979">
<l>perumai perumita miṉmai ciṟumai</l>
<l>perumita mūrntu viṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Freedom from conceit is (the nature of true) greatness (while) obstinacy therein is (that of) meanness.</l>
            </lg>
